Package Data.Entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BOM
    Bill of materials - is instantiated in BOMCalculator and used in ShowRequestCommand which puts the BOM on request attribute so it can be accessed in jsp-files
    Carport
    Mirrors carport table in database, is used in data mappers where a carport is returned and forwarded to the presentation layer where it is used in connection with request-handling.
    LineItem
    This class represents a line item in the bill of materials, is used in the logic layer where an instance is returned and later fetched and added to a list of lineitems (BOM).
    Material
    Mirrors material-tables in database, is used in data mappers where materials are fetched, and are then forwarded to logic layer, where it is added to a line item.
    PersonalInfo
    Mirrors users_personalinfo table in database, is used in data mappers where a user, and thereby, info is inserted / fetched.
    PrebuiltCarport
    Mirrors prebuilt_carport table in database, is instantiated and used in PrebuiltCarportCommand, where a list of prebuilt carport is set on the request attribute and later accessed in jsp-file.
    Request
    Mirrors requests table in database, is used in data mappers where a request is inserted/fetched, and in presentation layer where a request is created based on user-input or a request is fetched and displayed in jsp-file.
    Response
    Mirrors response table in database.
    Roof
    Mirrors roof-tables in database, is used in datamappers where it is fetched / inserted, and in presentation layer where the different rooftypes are displayed in jsp's, and roofs are instantiated in connection with requests.
    Shed
    Mirrors shed table in database, is used in data mappers where it is fetched/inserted and is used in presentation layer in connection with requests.
    ShippingAddress
    Mirrors shipping_address table in database, is associated with a user, and therefore, is used in data mappers when handling users, and in presentation layer, when info about a user is needed.
    ShoppingCart
    Instantiated in ShopCommand, where a session containing a shoppingCart is created
    User
    Mirrors user table in database, is used in data mappers when users are fetched/inserted and is used in presentation layer where a user is fetched when logging in and is stored on the session - Also used when a user registers in the system, where it is inserted in through user mapper.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Type
    An enum, which describes a type of material, is used in presentation layer where lineitems in bill of material is sorted into categories based on its type.
